sections.body:
Five one-syllable alias words can be assigned to anything and reused for a conversation:

A1 = {{dict:alias:1.word}} · A2 = {{dict:alias:2.word}} · A3 = {{dict:alias:3.word}} · A4 = {{dict:alias:4.word}} · A5 = {{dict:alias:5.word}}

Assign with 𐑽 (borrowed word) or 𐑸 (native phrase), close with the alias word. Once assigned, aliases take any prefix like a regular root.
